cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation tasks and proposes a method to incorporate source dependencies into the Transformer model. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training a model to learn source dependency relations in a supervised manner. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks, and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it deals with natural language processing tasks.
